### Test Laravel Sanctum Backend
### Make sure your Laravel server is running: php artisan serve

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login and get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get authenticated user (replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with actual token from login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

### 4. Test CORS - this should work from allowed origins
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Origin: http://localhost:3000
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json
